# Git sync with GitHub

Local `main` and `origin/main` must always match.

- Before starting work: `git fetch origin` and pull if behind.
- After completing work: commit and push so GitHub has the same code as local.
- Never leave the workspace diverged (ahead/behind) without telling the user.
- If a merge is in progress locally, resolve it — do not ask the user to merge manually.
